beer.beer_description:
If beer was a mythical kingdom, there’s no doubt that stout would rule the realm. Dark, earthy, biscuity, and timeless —it’s our brewer’s favourite for good reason. Our latest rye stout pairs complexity with drinkability... no tricks, no spins... just great, straight-up stout, just as it should be.
Each year Little Creatures brews a winter stout, each with their own variation, loved by many. 2023 isn’t any different. Off the back of the success of last year’s stout, we are again delivering.
